<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 負責保存流亡者記錄並分析戰前數據，確保沒有任何有價值的東西隨時間流失。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.title>檔案管理員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.titleShort>檔案管理員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Archivist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 維持巡邏隊和營地之間的無線電聯繫，協調任務並在荒地上傳遞重要訊息。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.title>傳訊官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.titleShort>通訊官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Communications_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 為被放逐者的營地提供食物，用任何能撿到的東西準備食物，並透過每餐來鼓舞士氣。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.title>被遺棄的廚師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.titleShort>廚師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Cook.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 專門從事爆炸物、清除障礙和破壞敵方防禦工事以進行流亡者行動。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.title>爆破專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>拆除</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 與荒地定居點和敵對派系進行談判，結盟並為流亡者的生存獲取資源。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.title>被遺棄的外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.titleShort>外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Diplomat.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 不斷晉升，指揮流亡者小隊，以戰術精確度協調攻擊和防禦行動。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.title>戰地指揮官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.titleShort>指揮官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Commander.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 向流亡者新兵傳授荒地生存的嚴酷現實，從覓食到野外維修和戰鬥訓練。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.title>現場講師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.titleShort>講師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Instructor.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 前往荒地研究變異的動植物群，為流亡者提供寶貴的科學見解和生存知識。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.title>實地研究員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.titleShort>研究員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Field_Researcher.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在武器操作、戰術和生存方面訓練新的流亡者新兵，塑造下一代戰士。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.title>講師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.titleShort>講師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Instructor.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 協調流亡者營地之間的物資和人員流動，確保每個小隊都有生存和戰鬥所需的東西。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.title>物流主任</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.titleShort>後勤</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Logistics_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 維護流亡者的車輛和設備，確保每台機器都做好隨時戰鬥的準備。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.title>被遺棄的機械師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.titleShort>機械</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Mechanic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 成為一名熟練的醫生，治療受傷的流亡者並開發新的野戰醫學技術以在荒地生存。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.title>醫務官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.titleShort>軍醫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Medical_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 成為維護和駕駛動力裝甲的專家，帶領流亡者衝鋒進入最危險的戰鬥。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.title>動力裝甲專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.titleShort>裝甲專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Power_Armor_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 管理流亡者的軍械庫和補給品，確保每個小隊都有生存和戰鬥所需的裝備。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.title>軍需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.titleShort>軍需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Quartermaster.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 擅長偵察敵人陣地和收集情報，經常為流亡者冒險深入敵對領土。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.title>偵察專家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>偵察</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 帶領探險隊進入危險的廢墟，回收寶貴的技術和資源，以確保流亡者的供應和運作。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.title>被遺棄的打撈者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.titleShort>打撈者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Salvager.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 帶領偵察隊穿過廢墟，繪製安全路線並在攻擊流亡者之前識別威脅。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.title>偵察隊長</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.titleShort>偵察隊長</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scout_Captain.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 致力於 [PAWN_possessive] 的一生來保存流亡者的知識並對每項恢復的技術和知識進行編目。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.title>被遺棄的抄寫員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.titleShort>隸</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Scribe.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 早年花費 [PAWN_possessive] 幫助流亡者檔案管理員保存和研究戰前文件，了解歷史和記錄保存的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>檔案員助理</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>檔案管理員</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在流亡者的地下掩體中出生長大，從小就學習紀律、謹慎和每一種資源的價值。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>地堡誕生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>地堡誕生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 被分配到流亡者的醫療艙，學習了基本的急診和分診，為前線的現實生活做好準備。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.title>戰地軍醫鄉紳</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>戰地醫療兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在車間度過了 [PAWN_possessive] 童年，學習修理和維護流放者的技術和車輛，確保他們的運作順利進行。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.title>被遺棄的機械師</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.titleShort>機械</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mechanic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 透過協助被遺棄的醫務人員學習了醫學基礎知識，培養了急救和傷員護理技能。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.title>被遺棄的醫生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.titleShort>軍醫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 透過在流亡者的食堂幫助組織膳食和補給品，確保每個人都有飯吃，學會了責任感和團隊合作。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>食堂管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>混亂管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>著迷於動力裝甲，[PAWN_nameDef]花了無數時間學習維護並最終操作這些流亡者力量的象徵。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>動力裝甲實習生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>鎧甲實習生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 曾接受偵察兵訓練，學習在荒地中航行並收集敵人動向的情報，確保兄弟會流亡者的安全。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.title>被遺棄的偵察兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.titleShort>偵察</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在年輕的童軍中扮演了領導角色，引導他們穿越荒地並教導他們生存所需的技能。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.title>被遺棄的童子軍領袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.titleShort>童軍領袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scout_Leader.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 被一位被遺棄的抄寫員選中作為早期指導，學習閱讀、寫作和分析古代文本和圖表。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>文士的學生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>文士的學生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 負責在流亡者營地之間運送物資，了解在嚴酷的荒地中速度和可靠性的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.title>被遺棄的補給跑者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.titleShort>供應跑者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Supply_Runner.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 很早就展現了技術天賦，協助 Outcast 工程師搶救和恢復戰前裝備。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>科技學徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>科技學徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.description>由於荒原的危險而成為孤兒，[PAWN_nameDef] 被流亡者收養，並很快適應了他們嚴酷的生存主義生活方式。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.title>廢土孤兒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.titleShort>孤兒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.description>小時候，[PAWN_nameDef] 經常出現在流亡者的工作室中，在資深機械師的指導下學習修理武器和盔甲。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.title>工作坊幫手</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.titleShort>工作坊幫手</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Workshop_Helper.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 一直對人類歷史感興趣，這讓 [PAWN_possessive] 被遺棄的老師很惱火，他們更喜歡教授更多「實用」的東西。 [PAWN_pronoun] 經常透過非傳統方式獲取知識。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.title>年輕歷史學家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.titleShort>歷史學家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Squire_Youngling_Historian.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 成為了以土地為生的專家，教導其他人如何狩獵、覓食以及忍受荒地可能提供的最惡劣的條件。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.title>生存主義者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.titleShort>生存主義者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Survivalist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 贏得了流亡者營地堅定保護者的聲譽，以堅定不移的決心堅守陣線，對抗掠奪者和變種人。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.title>老將後衛</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.titleShort>後衛</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Outcasts_Veteran_Defender.titleShort>
</LanguageData>
